00:40:32,894 --> 00:40:34,770
Ave Rei Bjorn!

354
00:40:34,771 --> 00:40:37,441
<i>Ave Rei Bjorn!</i>

355
00:41:22,944 --> 00:41:24,821
<i>Por que quer lutar?</i>

356
00:41:28,992 --> 00:41:30,744
