358
00:41:47,552 --> 00:41:48,952
Poder.

359
00:41:49,679 --> 00:41:52,556
<i>Poder é sempre perigoso.</i>

360
00:41:52,557 --> 00:41:54,434
<i>Atrai os piores</i>

361
00:41:55,018 --> 00:41:57,062
